\par \pard\plain \s38\sa120\nowidctlpar \f4\lang2057 {\i Pow!} works with Microsoft Win95, Win98 and Windows NT 4.0. Your computer must have at least 16 Megabytes of memory and a 80486DX Intel processor or better.
