\par \pard\plain \s38\sa120\nowidctlpar \f4\lang2057 Programs are written using a multi-document editor and compiled and linked together using the other integrated tools. The picture on the next page shows a typical screen layout when working with {\i Pow!}
. In this example some files are opened for editing and the message-window contains the output of the last compile-process.
