\par }\pard\plain \s38\sa120\nowidctlpar \f4\lang2057 To generate the executable select the menu entry {\i Compile/Make}. Alternatively, function key {\i F9} or the {\cs41\strike\cf11 make speed-button}{\v ProgrammingEnvironment} can be used.
\par The programming environment takes care of all actions necessary to create the program. Compiler and linker output is displayed in a message window:
