\par \pard\plain \s32\qj\sa120\nowidctlpar \f4\lang1031 {\lang2057 Every dialog in the environment contains a help button that comes up with specific infor\-ma\-tion about the dialog elements. The help file covers all features of }{\i\lang2057 Pow!}{\lang2057 
 itself. It can also be accessed by the menu entry Help/Pow.
